body_html:
Note that I am in the process of deleting TensorFlow*Estimator, so I
wouldn't spend too much effort on it. It's been deprecated for a while --
please use Estimator directly.
On Sat, Oct 15, 2016 at 09:32 Christophe Faucon notifications@github.com
wrote:

you can get example code here, this is how I made it work (and figured out
what the problem was)
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/learn/python/learn/estimators/rnn_test.py

The main thing to notice is that you MUST have an input_op_fn even though
it is a python optional (the default operation currently does not work).

#4608 #4608
